    dc:description "FIGURES 73–82. Anaphothrips of Australia. (73) A. dubius tergites VI–VIII. A. epacrida 74–77: (74) male sternites; (75) male tergite IX; (76) antenna; (77) forewing base. A. exocarpi 78–79: (78) forewing base with meso & metanotum; (79) antenna. A, eremophilae 80-82: (80) antenna; (81) head; (82) tergites VI–VIII." ;
